    <div id="main">
     <h3>
      Recharge your R'Card
     </h3>
     <p>
      Adding Bear Bucks to your UCR R'Card is secure, quick and easy.
     </p>
     <p>
      When depositing money to your R'Card you are working with a UCR partner, Blackboard.
                  Adding Bear Bucks is done on the Blackboard Commerce website. The following steps
                  will guide you and ensure the transaction is secure.
     </p>
     <table border="0" class="timeline" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 14px;">
      <tbody>
       <tr>
        <td>
         <ul>
          <li>
           Click on the
           <a href="https://eacct-ucrcard-sp.blackboard.com/BearBucks" target="_blank">
            Login to your Card Account
           </a>
           button below.
          </li>
          <li>
           Login with your UCR campus NetID.
          </li>
          <li>
           You will see the UCR Central Authentication login screen. Make sure the URL and login
                                 screen look like the image to the right.
          </li>
         </ul>
        </td>
        <td>
         <a class="fancybox" href="../images/cas.png">
          <img alt="step 1" class="img_R highslide" height="237" src="../images/cas_thumb.png" width="250"/>
         </a>
        </td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
        <td>
         <ul>
          <li>
           After you log-in you will be sent to the
           <a href="https://eacct-ucrcard-sp.blackboard.com/BearBucks" target="_blank">
            UCR R'Card partner page
           </a>
           .
          </li>
          <li>
           Make sure the URL and the card management screen look like the image to the right.
          </li>
          <li>
           Complete your transaction on the Blackboard Commerce Site.
          </li>
         </ul>
        </td>
        <td>
         <a class="fancybox" href="../images/blackboard.png">
          <img alt="step 2" class="img_R highslide" height="147" src="../images/blackboard_thumb.jpg" width="250"/>
         </a>
        </td>
       </tr>
      </tbody>
     </table>
     <table style="width: 400px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 24px;">
      <tbody>
       <tr>
        <td>
         <a href="https://eacct-ucrcard-sp.blackboard.com/BearBucks" target="_blank">
          <img alt="login" src="../images/loginbutton.png"/>
         </a>
        </td>
        <td>
         <a href="https://eacct-ucrcard-sp.blackboard.com/BearBucks">
          <img alt="deposit" src="../images/depositbutton.png"/>
         </a>
        </td>
       </tr>
      </tbody>
     </table>
